{"tid":122422,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"裁減本港約20名主要為支援GBM業務的資訊科技部(IT)員工","createTime":"2017-02-16T04:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T09:26:25.000Z","uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40e2d3208a071de08d15068dcff4c423d0aa7dec","tid":122422,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"IT狗, 有個電字就關你事架啦!!!<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n據本港報章引述消息報道，匯豐銀行今日(16日)裁減本港約20名環球銀行及資本市場業務(GBM，俗稱炒房)員工。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》引該行員工消息稱，受影響員工昨晚(15日)起陸續收到通知，大部分於中環總行上班，主要為支援GBM業務的資訊科技部(IT)員工，該部門的IT員工昨日亦曾舉行會議，討論未來的資源調配事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.784800/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.784800%2F1&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ab3341ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.784800/1</a>"},{"pid":"d3595643e0dfa01f22bd4cc49814efcc3e357487","tid":122422,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eb6f9417a8d7b8ccbc80b3bcf6589160682a31","tid":122422,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"IT 部俾人炒是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}